      </p>
    </Line>
    <Line>
      <p>
        Refunds. If you are dissatisfied for any reason, you may request a full refund within 60 days of the order date. Contact us at support@terminal.shop with your order details.
      </p>
    </Line>
    <Line>
      <p>
        <span class="text-white">3. Shipping, Risk of Loss & Delivery</span>
      </p>
    </Line>
    <Line>
      <p>
        Carrier & Timing. Orders typically ship within one (1) business day and are delivered within one (1) week of shipment. Delivery dates are estimates and not guaranteed.
      </p>
    </Line>
    <Line>
